再收了<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"395691eef0cb8c119b08bc71d3ef63f7ad2059c7","tid":688096,"uid":61018,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T01:48:39.000Z","msg":"世界冠軍球會盃係咪阿里巴巴贊助?"},{"pid":"07ca543c49aa1c8fe0b619d828eb41afa94f3d19","tid":688096,"uid":10890,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T02:04:14.000Z","msg":"一個日本人、一個韓國人和一個支那人有幸見到了上帝。<br />\n<br />\n日本人問上帝：「我們日本甚麼時候能獲得世界盃足球賽的冠軍？」上帝說：「100年。」日本人哭了：「嗚嗚嗚&hellip;&hellip;我這輩子是看不到了！」<br />\n<br />\n韓國人也問上帝：「韓國甚麼時候能獲得世界盃冠軍？」上帝答：「也許200年吧。」韓國人也哭了：「嗚嗚嗚&hellip;&hellip;我下一輩子也看不到了！」<br />\n<br />\n支那人當然也問上帝：「我們<span style=\"font-size: small;\">兒</span>中國<span style=\"font-size: small;\">兒</span>什麼<span style=\"font-size: small;\">兒</span>時候<span style=\"font-size: small;\">兒</span>能<span style=\"font-size: small;\">兒</span>獲得世界盃<span style=\"font-size: small;\">兒</span>冠軍？」這時候，上帝哭了：「嗚嗚嗚&hellip;&hellip;我是看不到了！」"},{"pid":"dcda38b9848f35666e3e5d670f5ebf8bd08db2ab","tid":688096,"uid":158270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T02:10:54.000Z","msg":"劇本：砸錢申辦世界盃，然後收買球證。"},{"pid":"5693937b3394542ff5db9acac4f2382b54889553","tid":688096,"uid":25345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T02:37:40.000Z","msg":"2050 贏到世盃<br />\n我個年差唔多拿mpf 睇到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"acdfc7c2ab68c4b9ae002d779761780e91ae8fb7","tid":688096,"uid":550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5693937b3394542ff5db9acac4f2382b54889553","tid":688096,"uid":25345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T02:37:40.000Z","msg":"2050 贏到世盃<br />\n我個年差唔多拿mpf 睇到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/face